The sound of missiles alerted him, and he managed to avoid all attacks
from Vehement and Unicron. He moved away however SkullGrin's shots hit.
"Ahhhhhhh!"
He droped down, but got back up. He came up behind SkullGrin, and sent a
kick to the back of his head.
